            <title>[LUCENE-3024] If index has more than Integer.MAX_VALUE terms, seeking can it AIOOBE due to long/int overflow</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3024</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Tom hit a new long/int overflow case: &lt;a href=&quot;http://markmail.org/thread/toyl2ujcl4suqvf3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot;&gt;http://markmail.org/thread/toyl2ujcl4suqvf3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

